# Runtime, generated proof, and historic design archives are local-only.
.runtime/
.codex-runs/
node_modules/
apps/web/dist-vercel/
docs/auto-execute/
docs/backup/
docs/UI/1/
docs/UI/2/
docs/UI/小程序/
docs/*.md
docs/UI/web/*.png
docs/UI/web/*.md

# The deployment build copies these user-supplied production assets into the
# static web output.  Keep exactly these inputs available to the build.
!docs/
!docs/UI/
!docs/UI/web/
!docs/UI/web/pic/
!docs/UI/web/pic/**
!docs/UI/web/icon/
!docs/UI/web/icon/many-worlds-icons-clean/
!docs/UI/web/icon/many-worlds-icons-clean/png-tight/
!docs/UI/web/icon/many-worlds-icons-clean/png-tight/**
!docs/UI/web/game/
!docs/UI/web/game/**
